                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman</hi>). I produce a certificate of the prisoner's former conviction—(<hi rend="italic">read—Convicted March, 1849, and confined nine months</hi>)—he is the man—I found his lodging in a very bad condition—he has been in custody several times.</p>
